title: Embakasi South Sub County Holds a Public Participation Forum (Nairobi City County)
text: ( Source : Nairobi City County ) Embakasi South Sub County Holds a Public Participation Forum Residents of Embakasi South Sub County on 30th September , 2015 participated in a Public Participation forum organized by the Sub County
